Lord Shao Cang is in the Lunar Sect.

14
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:34,060
Why are you all looking at me?

15
00:01:34,570 --> 00:01:35,430
It won't do me any good

16
00:01:35,430 --> 00:01:36,350
