17
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:36,990
I don't want to be locked

18
00:01:36,990 --> 00:01:38,920
in the Spirit-Sealing Formation.

19
00:01:39,509 --> 00:01:41,130
I'll make some noise down the mountain

20
00:01:41,130 --> 00:01:42,190
and lure them away.

21
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:44,509
Don't go.

22
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,870
The Great Path Sect has a clear goal this time.

23
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:47,600
I think

24
00:01:47,910 --> 00:01:48,750
they won't

25
00:01:48,770 --> 00:01:49,890
retreat easily.

26
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:52,050
I'm familiar with the Lunar Sect.

27
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:52,830
Next,

28
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,410
listen to my arrangement.

29
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,120
Don't act on your own.

30
00:01:59,990 --> 00:02:00,930
I have an idea.

31
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:01,750
I agree.

32
00:02:03,670 --> 00:02:04,230
Brother.

33
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:05,230
Take this with you.

34
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:05,860
For self-defense.

35
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:06,280
Okay.

36
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:09,199
Come with me.

37
00:02:10,509 --> 00:02:11,310
What about me?

38
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,620
You...

39
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:13,950
Find a place to hide.

40
00:02:13,950 --> 00:02:15,550
Just don't let them skin you.

41
00:02:32,450 --> 00:02:34,890
It's so noisy.

42
00:02:37,090 --> 00:02:38,860
Whose dog is so arrogant?

43
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:42,710
Disturbing my sleep.

44
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,220
Oh, it's just you, Zhu.

45
00:02:53,930 --> 00:02:55,930
We're here at the premier's order

46
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:57,880
to capture the rebel Shao Cang.

47
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:00,840
Please do us a favor

48
00:03:01,290 --> 00:03:03,000
and let us search thoroughly.

49
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,210
What if

50
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,820
I refuse?

51
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:11,580
If this delays the Great Path's plan

52
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:13,830
and receives the Premier's blame,

53
00:03:14,170 --> 00:03:16,230
your father won't be able to help you.

54
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:19,220
Elder Zhu.

55
00:03:19,790 --> 00:03:21,550
At a time like this,

56
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:23,470
you should worry about yourself.

57
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:25,600
Your trip this time

58
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,320
not only disturbed the civilians

59
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,650
but also provoked the established sects.

60
00:03:29,790 --> 00:03:31,120
Aren't you afraid of ruining

61
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,110
Great Path's reputation?

62
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:33,790
What if Premier fires you

63
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:34,910
in a fit of rage?

64
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,720
Don’t worry about that.

65
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,940
I have a clear conscience.

66
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,760
Premier will understand.

67
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:43,730
Right.

68
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,910
Anyway, Great Path

69
00:03:45,930 --> 00:03:47,730
has no reputation to begin with.

70
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:50,590
Seems like we can only

71
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,760
settle this by force.

72
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,340
Let's see who dares to come forward.

73
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,050
Go in and have a look.

74
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,670
Search carefully.

75
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,170
[Five-Poison Heart Pill]

76
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:06,720
[Ji Yang]

77
00:05:00,550 --> 00:05:02,280
It's Shao Cang's handwriting.

78
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:05,860
Let’s report it to the Elder.

79
00:05:09,170 --> 00:05:09,930
Junior Mo.

80
00:05:13,350 --> 00:05:14,730
If Shao Cang wrote this,

81
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:15,910
he might be nearby.

82
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:17,890
Go report to the Elder.

83
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:20,640
I'll lead the team and continue to search around.

84
00:05:22,530 --> 00:05:24,390
Young Lord Mu, you keep trying to keep us at bay.

85
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:25,590
Could there really be

86
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:27,890
something suspicious in the closet?

87
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,900
Since you know it,

88
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:34,930
why are you forcing me?

89
00:05:37,710 --> 00:05:39,110
Let me tell you the truth.

90
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:41,560
It's not that I don't want to open it for you.

91
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,310
I'm just afraid that after I open it,

92
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,830
you'll see something you shouldn't see

93
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:46,830
and hurt our peace.

94
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,870
[Premier of Great Path Sect, Ying Zewei]

95
00:05:51,890 --> 00:05:54,440
[Premier of Great Path Sect, Ying Zewei]

96
00:05:59,220 --> 00:06:03,980
[Premier of Great Path Sect, Ying Zewei]

97
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:13,080
How dare you disrespect

98
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:15,550
Premier this way?

99
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:17,170
My goodness.

100
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:18,800
My confidant!

101
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:20,340
Elder Zhu,

102
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:21,880
this painting is my treasure.

103
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,160
I've shown it to many people.

104
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:26,830
[Premier of Great Path Sect, Ying Zewei]

105
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:24,180
Only you

106
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:25,630
can recognize at a glance

107
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:26,960
that this is Ying Zewei.

108
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,590
It seems that you not only know painting,

109
00:06:29,590 --> 00:06:30,530
but also me

110
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:32,200
and your master.

111
00:06:32,409 --> 00:06:34,050
His name is written on it.

112
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:35,360
Do you think I'm blind?

113
00:06:37,330 --> 00:06:38,770
[Premier of Great Path Sect, Ying Zewei]

114
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:41,220
I'm sorry.

115
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:41,909
Look at me.

116
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:42,690
I forgot.

117
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:43,190
No.

118
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:44,360
I wrote it there because most people

119
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,760
couldn't recognize him.

120
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:48,080
Young Lord Mu.

121
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:52,490
[Premier of Great Path Sect, Ying Zewei]

122
00:06:49,010 --> 00:06:50,330
Don't go too far.

123
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,530
This is not the East Sea.

124
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:53,540
Yes.

125
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,159
Elder Zhu.

126
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:55,010
Calm down.

127
00:06:55,030 --> 00:06:56,420
Calm down.

128
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:57,350
Since you

129
00:06:57,350 --> 00:06:58,670
have such discerning eyes,

130
00:06:58,670 --> 00:06:59,760
why don't you guess

131
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:00,530
who this is?

132
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,460
Look.

133
00:07:10,590 --> 00:07:11,540
Your father?

134
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,260
Elder Zhu.

135
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:22,510
You are really my confidant!

136
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:23,760
Elder Zhu.

137
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:26,620
Elder Zhu.

138
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:28,320
I’ve been studying

139
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:29,960
this kind of beast style recently.

140
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:31,340
It emphasizes simplicity.

141
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:32,350
A few strokes

142
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:34,670
can draw out the essence of the character.

143
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:35,230
Elder Zhu,

144
00:07:35,230 --> 00:07:36,350
if you are interested,

145
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:37,820
I can draw one for you.

146
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:38,360
It's very fast.

147
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,440
It won't take long.

148
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:40,300
No need!

149
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:44,820
Young Lord Mu, you'd better save your talent

150
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:46,480
for your father's portraits.

151
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,940
[Premier of Great Path Sect, Ying Zewei]

152
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:54,550
Elder Zhu!

153
00:07:54,710 --> 00:07:56,020
Think about it!

154
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:57,670
I'm fast!

155
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:03,200
Elder Zhu.

156
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:04,750
Elder Zhu.

157
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,290
This man humiliated Premier.

158
00:08:06,290 --> 00:08:07,620
Should we just let it go?

159
00:08:08,290 --> 00:08:10,290
Let's not argue with those below us.

160
00:08:10,730 --> 00:08:12,660
The Great Path is better than that.

161
00:08:13,230 --> 00:08:13,710
Yes.

162
00:08:21,910 --> 00:08:22,890
I'll take care of them.

163
00:08:22,890 --> 00:08:23,550
You go first.

164
00:08:23,550 --> 00:08:24,360
No.

165
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:25,930
I was the one who kept you.

166
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,670
This happened all because of me.

167
00:08:27,670 --> 00:08:29,400
If the entire sect is implicated

168
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:30,730
because of this,

169
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:32,440
then Mu Zhanting, Yin Ya,

170
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:33,870
Chief, and even Meng Ying

171
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:35,140
will all be killed.

172
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,789
Once Great Path's people

173
00:08:36,789 --> 00:08:37,669
find you,

174
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:38,750
the Lunar Sect

175
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:39,309
will also be guilty

176
00:08:39,309 --> 00:08:40,590
of hiding a fugitive.

177
00:08:40,830 --> 00:08:41,480
Don't worry.

178
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,010
I will clarify everything.

179
00:08:43,210 --> 00:08:44,590
The reason I'm here at Lunar Sect

180
00:08:44,590 --> 00:08:45,860
is because I forced you

181
00:08:45,890 --> 00:08:47,270
to hide me here.

182
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:48,790
Lunar Sect was unaware.

183
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:50,240
This matter

184
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:53,040
has nothing to do with the Lunar Sect.

185
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,510
You don't have to take responsibility for me.

186
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,720
In their eyes,

187
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,950
you are a treacherous and

188
00:08:56,950 --> 00:08:58,280
untrustworthy person.

189
00:08:58,740 --> 00:08:59,940
If you suddenly cut us

190
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:01,080
off like this,

191
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:02,710
can't they tell that

192
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:04,470
you want to protect us instead?

193
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,280
If you really care about us

194
00:09:06,310 --> 00:09:07,870
and don't want me to take the blame for you,

195
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:08,990
just stay here and

196
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:10,080
don't go anywhere.

197
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:11,410
You just said that

198
00:09:11,410 --> 00:09:12,670
the Great Path Sect is hard to fool.

199
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:13,670
Since they are here,

200
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:15,070
they won't leave easily.

201
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:16,880
If anything happens to you,

202
00:09:17,530 --> 00:09:18,990
I'll let them die with you.

203
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:20,930
If you really kill

204
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:21,950
Zhu Sui and the rest today,

205
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:23,830
you'll fall right into their hands.

206
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:24,390
You'd really be found guilty

207
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:26,070
of slaughtering your fellow disciples.

208
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:26,770
By then,

209
00:09:26,830 --> 00:09:28,590
the entire cultivation realm will be your enemy.

210
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:29,350
There are so many people,

211
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:30,550
can you kill them all?

212
00:09:36,010 --> 00:09:37,160
No matter what happens,

213
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,290
you must not show up.

214
00:09:41,650 --> 00:09:42,650
This belongs to your mother.

215
00:09:42,650 --> 00:09:43,660
You can't give it to outsiders.

216
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:44,990
You are not an outsider.

217
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,000
Miss,

218
00:10:22,310 --> 00:10:22,890
why are you

219
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:24,210
in this forest alone?

220
00:10:25,290 --> 00:10:26,350
I'm catching some venomous insects

221
00:10:26,350 --> 00:10:27,350
to make medicine.

222
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:35,590
Did you plant those Vermilion flower

223
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:37,120
at the foot of the mountain?

224
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,660
You know poison too?

225
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:41,230
A fellow of the same craft.

226
00:10:41,230 --> 00:10:42,290
I know a little.

227
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:44,720
May I ask

228
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,660
who lives in that room with you?

229
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:50,310
I've been studying poison.

230
00:10:50,310 --> 00:10:51,500
I'm always alone.

231
00:10:51,610 --> 00:10:52,890
Who would live with me?

232
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:54,310
Young Master.

233
00:10:54,850 --> 00:10:56,150
It seems that you know poison too.

234
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:57,510
Why don't you stay

235
00:10:57,650 --> 00:10:59,970
and make medicine with me?

236
00:11:00,010 --> 00:11:01,060
What do you think?

237
00:11:02,090 --> 00:11:03,870
I am Mo Xingzheng, a disciple of the Great Path.

238
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:05,730
I was ordered to search for a fugitive here.

239
00:11:05,730 --> 00:11:06,280
If you

240
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,690
see any suspicious person,

241
00:11:07,690 --> 00:11:08,940
please inform me.

242
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:11,440
A suspicious person?

243
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:15,830
I think you are suspicious.

244
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,270
You sneaked into the yard

245
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,650
while the master of the house was absent.

246
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:19,980
That's akin to a robber.

247
00:11:20,070 --> 00:11:21,470
You asked a stranger woman

248
00:11:21,470 --> 00:11:22,800
about her private life.

249
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:24,290
That's akin to a hooligan.

250
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:26,440
You broke into our sect

251
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,060
and wandered around as you like.

252
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:29,390
That's akin to a bandit.

253
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,450
You misunderstood.

254
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:32,400
Misunderstood?

255
00:11:32,830 --> 00:11:34,210
If I remember correctly,

256
00:11:34,210 --> 00:11:35,080
a few days ago,

257
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:37,040
you already searched the place, right?

258
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:38,190
In just a few days,

259
00:11:38,310 --> 00:11:40,090
you intrude on our sect twice.

260
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:41,540
What?

261
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:43,140
Do you want to

262
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:45,370
ransack our sect while you're at it?

263
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:47,190
Unfortunately,

264
00:11:47,430 --> 00:11:48,390
I'm so poor that

265
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:50,390
I only have these precious insects.

266
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:52,010
Have you thought it through?

267
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:52,940
Do you want them?

268
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:54,730
No need.

269
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:55,960
I shall take my leave.

270
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:31,430
How was it?

271
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,330
Don't worry.

272
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:33,520
That’s good.

273
00:12:33,830 --> 00:12:34,890
Where is Elder Zhu?

274
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,270
Don't mention it.

275
00:12:36,270 --> 00:12:36,950
Zhu

276
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:38,840
was so mad that he almost fainted.

277
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,310
All disciples of the Lunar Sect,

278
00:12:41,310 --> 00:12:43,240
gather at the square immediately.

279
00:12:44,710 --> 00:12:46,430
I have something to ask.

280
00:12:48,050 --> 00:12:49,240
Who does he think he is?

281
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,680
He acts like he's such a big deal all the time.

282
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:52,480
I'll roast him with the Sun Fire.

283
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:53,280
Calm down.

284
00:12:54,290 --> 00:12:55,550
He is not a good person.

285
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:56,810
The chief is not here now.

286
00:12:56,810 --> 00:12:58,720
If we confront him head-on, there will only be trouble.

287
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,390
How about

288
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:00,410
playing it by ear?

289
00:13:00,450 --> 00:13:02,780
We'll talk about it when Chief comes back.

290
00:13:02,870 --> 00:13:04,000
This lucky bastard.

291
00:13:04,950 --> 00:13:06,280
Let's go and have a look.

