300
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:58,830
Ji Yang

301
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,280
is Shao Cang.

302
00:14:06,690 --> 00:14:07,800
[Ji Yang]

303
00:14:09,810 --> 00:14:11,220
[Ji Yang]

304
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:15,140
Don't blame me for not reminding you.

305
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:17,970
The rebel Shao Cang

306
