307
00:14:20,830 --> 00:14:23,430
He won't even spare the people of the same clan,

308
00:14:23,650 --> 00:14:25,290
let alone your lot

309
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:27,610
who have nothing to do with him.

310
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:31,970
The ignorant is innocent.

311
00:14:32,230 --> 00:14:33,120
Today,

312
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:35,780
whoever reveals Shao Cang’s whereabouts,

313
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:37,880
will not only be spared,

314
00:14:38,350 --> 00:14:39,820
but also heavily rewarded.

315
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:41,820
If you conceal the truth on purpose,

316
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,910
