319
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:53,280
Show yourself if you dare...

320
00:14:53,990 --> 00:14:55,570
Was it not the fox spirit that day,

321
00:14:55,570 --> 00:14:56,670
but Lord Shao Cang?

322
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:05,720
Senior!

323
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:09,710
Where is Ji Yang?

324
00:15:11,430 --> 00:15:14,070
I don't know.

325
00:15:21,370 --> 00:15:22,240
