326
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:25,360
Senior!

327
00:15:25,690 --> 00:15:26,320
Senior!

328
00:15:26,430 --> 00:15:27,450
Are you alright?

329
00:15:29,020 --> 00:15:29,850
Elder Zhu.

330
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:32,330
The person you are looking for

331
00:15:33,410 --> 00:15:33,990
