333
00:15:37,310 --> 00:15:38,170
It's you again.

334
00:15:38,820 --> 00:15:40,220
Are you kidding me again?

335
00:15:40,950 --> 00:15:43,140
How can I joke with you, Elder Zhu?

336
00:15:43,180 --> 00:15:44,390
You are the one

337
00:15:44,390 --> 00:15:45,180
joking here.

338
00:15:45,950 --> 00:15:46,990
Elder Zhu, look.

339
00:15:48,390 --> 00:15:48,950
Here.

340
00:15:49,070 --> 00:15:49,910
Great Path's Lord Shao Cang

341
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:51,530
is nowhere to be seen.

342
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:53,780
To be honest,

343
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:55,390
I wrote

344
00:15:56,570 --> 00:15:57,750
these words.

345
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,810
[Ji Yang]

346
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:25,830
How is that possible?

347
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:28,460
Thank you for your compliment.

348
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:29,220
It seems that

349
00:16:29,300 --> 00:16:30,950
my imitation of Shao Cang's handwriting

350
00:16:30,950 --> 00:16:32,060
has reached the level

351
00:16:32,060 --> 00:16:34,060
of being mistaken for the real deal.

352
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:35,010
Mr. Mu.

353
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:37,560
Why did you imitate Shao Cang's handwriting?

354
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:39,760
This must be new information for you.

355
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:42,130
Shao Cang’s calligraphy

356
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:43,680
