357
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:44,750
The strokes are lively

358
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:46,400
and absolutely striking.

359
00:16:46,430 --> 00:16:46,900
Wait.

360
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:48,460
What's wrong with imitating it?

361
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:49,510
Did I use your brush

362
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:50,810
