363
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:51,630
Seriously.

364
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,670
Mr. Mu is eloquent.

365
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:56,620
I admire that.

366
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:58,330
However,

367
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:00,920
