368
00:17:01,610 --> 00:17:02,280
Isn't he...

369
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:03,220
Well...

370
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,010
Who?

371
00:17:04,630 --> 00:17:05,750
Who? He...

372
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:07,609
I came here to study

373
00:17:07,829 --> 00:17:09,109
because the Lunar Sect

374
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:10,069
has Master Boyang's

375
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,310
Eternity Inner Canon.

376
00:17:11,310 --> 00:17:11,869
Recorded inside

377
00:17:11,869 --> 00:17:13,829
