378
00:17:13,829 --> 00:17:15,990
It can cure my mother's old illness.

379
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:16,589
So,

380
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:17,650
I found a patient

381
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:18,990
with a similar illness

382
00:17:18,990 --> 00:17:20,440
to my mother's.

383
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:22,319
This medicine tester

384
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:23,589
is called Ji Yang.

385
00:17:24,910 --> 00:17:26,109
We checked her room.

386
00:17:26,470 --> 00:17:27,220
It is indeed filled

387
00:17:27,220 --> 00:17:29,750
with venomous insects and poisonous plants.

388
00:17:33,370 --> 00:17:34,870
If it's a patient,

389
00:17:35,710 --> 00:17:37,140
why doesn't anyone in the

390
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,500
