391
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:41,790
The Lunar Sect has strict rules.

392
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:43,190
We can't hide outsiders.

393
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:44,550
So this person

394
00:17:44,730 --> 00:17:46,090
