395
00:17:46,360 --> 00:17:47,600
Where is he today?

396
00:17:48,110 --> 00:17:49,370
He's not in the sect today.

397
00:17:49,370 --> 00:17:51,170
Maybe he went down the mountain.

398
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:03,460
Have you

399
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:04,820
