400
00:18:06,470 --> 00:18:07,200
This person?

401
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:08,250
No.

402
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:09,870
No?

403
00:18:12,030 --> 00:18:12,920
No.

404
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,200
Really?

405
00:18:14,630 --> 00:18:15,880
No matter how many times you ask,

406
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,030
