407
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:17,830
Of course not.

408
00:18:22,270 --> 00:18:22,910
Fine.

409
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:24,960
But

410
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:26,930
you have no evidence.

411
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:30,340
If you have a clear conscience,

412
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:32,920
why don't you try my

413
00:18:32,990 --> 00:18:33,630
Celestial Lightning of Truth?

414
00:18:33,630 --> 00:18:34,310
No way!

415
00:18:34,310 --> 00:18:35,900
The Celestial Lightning of Truth?

416
00:18:35,900 --> 00:18:37,500
You're the Elder of Great Path.

417
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:38,270
