419
00:18:39,390 --> 00:18:40,180
Mu Zhanting!

420
00:18:40,430 --> 00:18:41,730
I've had enough of you!

421
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:42,840
Me too!

422
00:18:42,870 --> 00:18:44,070
