427
00:19:26,150 --> 00:19:27,060
Here we go.

428
00:19:27,650 --> 00:19:29,190
It's coming...

429
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:30,450
Coming!

430
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:33,790
Chief Meng.

431
00:19:34,050 --> 00:19:34,980
I found that when

432
00:19:34,990 --> 00:19:36,500
Nan Rao isn't here,

433
00:19:36,540 --> 00:19:37,870
you become really

434
00:19:38,230 --> 00:19:39,110
lucky.

435
00:19:39,210 --> 00:19:39,960
Of course.

436
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:42,150
I didn't read the The Sparrow's Nine Verses

437
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:43,750
Yingying gave me for naught.

438
00:19:44,470 --> 00:19:45,650
I told you.

439
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:48,310
Rao and I don't get along at the game table,

440
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:49,770
