441
00:19:50,350 --> 00:19:52,010
This is just an analysis, but,

442
00:19:52,690 --> 00:19:54,410
were you losing to her

443
00:19:54,470 --> 00:19:56,040
on purpose?

444
00:19:58,940 --> 00:20:00,110
Don't tell me...

445
00:20:00,580 --> 00:20:02,240
Are you in love with her?

446
00:20:03,610 --> 00:20:04,330
You...

447
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:06,020
My card!

448
00:20:07,930 --> 00:20:09,140
You can insult me,

449
00:20:09,410 --> 00:20:10,970
but not my sportsmanship.

450
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:11,590
Yes.

451
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:14,430
I saw you went to the back mountain,

452
00:20:14,430 --> 00:20:15,530
so I followed you.

453
00:20:15,950 --> 00:20:16,560
Yan

454
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:17,720
went after the people from

455
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,780
Great Path, right?

456
00:20:19,030 --> 00:20:20,690
Did she do it to lure them away?

457
00:20:24,330 --> 00:20:26,230
Yan is in danger

458
00:20:26,410 --> 00:20:27,490
because of you.

459
00:20:28,130 --> 00:20:29,990
Why don't we help her?

460
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:32,360
If we work together,

461
00:20:32,370 --> 00:20:33,510
I'm sure we can

462
00:20:34,180 --> 00:20:35,990
defeat them somehow.

463
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:42,710
W-what's wrong?

464
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:48,990
You wrote that

465
00:20:50,380 --> 00:20:51,840
