466
00:20:55,050 --> 00:20:55,630
Don't...

467
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:57,770
Don't kill me.

468
00:20:59,250 --> 00:21:00,830
Nan Yan treats you as his friend.

469
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:02,230
Is this how you treat her?

470
00:21:05,610 --> 00:21:06,430
Kid,

471
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,470
