474
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:11,640
Let go of me!

475
00:21:11,990 --> 00:21:13,050
You're shameless!

476
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:13,980
Let go of me!

477
00:21:14,020 --> 00:21:14,530
Let...

478
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:17,340
Don't hurt him.

479
00:21:17,490 --> 00:21:18,690
Come at me if you dare.

480
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:21,320
You're quite loyal.

481
00:21:22,010 --> 00:21:22,550
Fine.

482
00:21:23,470 --> 00:21:25,520
As long as you tell me where Shao Cang is,

483
00:21:25,520 --> 00:21:26,520
I promise

484
00:21:26,570 --> 00:21:27,560
I will release

485
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:28,350
