486
00:21:28,950 --> 00:21:30,150
I've never seen him.

487
00:21:30,170 --> 00:21:31,700
Why would I know where he is?

488
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:38,780
Nan Yan!

489
00:21:39,770 --> 00:21:40,770
Let go of me.

490
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:42,020
And let you die?

491
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:43,390
