500
00:21:59,910 --> 00:22:00,960
No.

501
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:02,410
No.

502
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:03,590
Fine.

503
00:22:04,860 --> 00:22:07,860
Since you are so stubborn,

504
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,900
