507
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:17,380
Senior.

508
00:22:17,630 --> 00:22:18,630
What should we do?

509
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:19,410
Don't move.

510
00:22:23,170 --> 00:22:25,110
Dispelling evil and warding off misfortune.

511
00:22:25,110 --> 00:22:27,840
Invoking lightning for righteous punishments.

512
00:23:02,660 --> 00:23:04,160
Let me ask you again.

513
00:23:04,860 --> 00:23:06,920
Have you ever seen Shao Cang?

514
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:08,200
Never.

515
00:23:09,390 --> 00:23:10,060
Fine.

516
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:11,330
Senior.

517
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:12,670
Senior, tell him to stop.

518
00:23:12,670 --> 00:23:14,090
