519
00:23:40,150 --> 00:23:42,080
The Celestial Lightning of Truth.

520
00:23:42,500 --> 00:23:43,510
Nan Yan.

521
00:23:46,270 --> 00:23:47,720
If I lie to you,

522
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:49,410
