543
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,960
I'll ask you one last time.

544
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:24,680
Have you ever seen Shao Cang?

545
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:29,240
Bear with it.

546
00:25:30,430 --> 00:25:31,790
Everything will be fine

547
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:33,420
