591
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:43,440
Meng Zhiguang!

592
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,040
How dare you hurt the judicial elder

593
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:46,540
of the Great Path Sect?

594
00:28:46,840 --> 00:28:48,080
