616
00:29:34,490 --> 00:29:35,480
Wayward disciple!

617
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,920
Hurry up and

618
00:29:36,950 --> 00:29:37,880
greet Elder Zhu.

619
00:29:38,650 --> 00:29:40,800
Don't blame me for hijacking you here.

620
00:29:41,370 --> 00:29:43,050
Help our sect get through this,

621
00:29:43,050 --> 00:29:44,720
