Because his illness is similar to her mother's,

632
00:30:13,430 --> 00:30:14,960
Nan Yan hid him in her quarters

633
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,770
to test treatments on him.

634
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,950
