656
00:31:20,230 --> 00:31:21,490
If I have to report

657
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:22,990
even such a small thing as

658
00:31:23,110 --> 00:31:25,390
keeping a spirit pet to the Great Path Sect,

659
00:31:25,390 --> 00:31:26,760
will there be anyone who dares

660
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,830
to raise chickens and livestock in the Five States?

661
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:29,850
